{"tid":1190281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩係間小食鋪聽到啲店員講反送中","createTime":"2019-06-07T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T08:40:11.000Z","uid":860,"like":27,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63d9aa2059d0c075f2425e0179ba8fee915d2645","tid":1190281,"uid":860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"一個有口音嘅阿姐問應該係老闆嘅人<br />\n阿姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁我地後日係咪唔開鋪去遊行呀？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無講野，舉左張紙<br />\n張紙寫住中立<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你讀出黎係咩字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔係中唔中立問題呀，有啲人真係好慘架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪搞事啦，出去啲人肯定係比人誤導<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係呢，好多啲鋪頭仔都唔開門出去遊行呀，真係好慘架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁係咪唔駛做生意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無再開口，淨係細細聲講，唉啲人好慘架，無啦啦捉左返大陸<br />\n<br />\n我係隔離食野聽到，成個人好錯愕<br />\n我當個有口音嘅阿姐係蝗呀，佢都識諗過個香港人老闆<br />\n點解仲有香港人覺得燒到黎都無問題<br />\n<br />\n大家6月9見"},{"pid":"7a990cedc12c5de99433dbe40048fe16158f544c","tid":1190281,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:39:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"307c31330da636b94e2e9c345036555351f031db","tid":1190281,"uid":42340,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T08:40:11.000Z","msg":"又作故仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}